article.description: — Emmanuel Ansong had 23 points as Green Bay beat Robert Morris 70-58 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Ansong lifts Green Bay over Robert Morris 70-58
article.linkText: Ansong lifts Green Bay over Robert Morris 70-58
article.story: GREEN BAY, Wis. -- — Emmanuel Ansong had 23 points as Green Bay beat Robert Morris 70-58 on Thursday night. The game was the Horizon League opener for both teams. Donovan Ivory had 11 points and seven rebounds for Green Bay (2-5). Japannah Kellogg III added 10 points. Lucas Stieber had six assists. Rasheem Dunn had 17 points for the Colonials (0-6). Justin Winston added 16 points. Enoch Cheeks had seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
